A Nigerian man has allegedly given his girlfriend the beating of her life. According to reports, the sad incident took place last week. It was gathered that the incident happened over alleged suspicion of infidelity at Flat 266, Tosam building, Jakande Estate, Lagos. . . The suspect who is said to be jobless was said to have instructed the victim to quit her job because he felt she’s dating her supervisor. The lady’s refusal angered him and he decided to assault her. Source